I am playing in character. If you'd remember, the last thing that
Wolfgang did (which is why he was put in the basement of the Alliance
base`, torture chamber actually), was declare that he was taking over
and kick Nemesis Enforcer out. I would say that's plenty cause to be
wary of him.

::FZ::

FZ laughs. "What else was I supposed to do with a traitor? I don't
appreciate people trying to take over, as several bots have found out
in the past."
